title: Ep. - 289 - TRAVIS MACY FROM WORLD’S TOUGHEST RACE: ECO-CHALLENGE FIJI LOVE ISLAND 90 DAY FIANCE: HAPPILY EVER AFTER REAL HOUSEWIVES OF POTOMAC
description:
Kate reviews this week on 90 Day Fiance: Happily Ever After and Real Housewives of Potomac.

 

Travis Macy from World's Toughest Race: Eco-Challenge Fiji, a tv series documenting a long-range multi-day expedition race in which teams race non-stop with little to no sleep over mountains, jungles, and oceans. The show is on Amazon Prime.

 

Sarah Fraser and Andrea Lopez, from the Hey Frase podcast review Love Island on CBS. The show, based on the UK super hit, involves a group of contestants, referred to as Islanders, living in isolation from the outside world in a villa, constantly under video surveillance.
